author: Huawei
description:
Taejae University is redefining what modern education by putting the learner at the center.
 
In this #TransformTalks conversation, President Dr. Jaeho Yeom joins Wang Hongzhen, #Huawei APAC Vice President of Government & Public Sector, to explore how AI is transforming education. From personalized learning pathways to automated administrative work, AI is freeing professors to focus less on paperwork and more on mentoring, guiding, and inspiring students.
 
Discover how technology is reshaping education around human potential at https://bit.ly/4jb1MLX #ThisIsHuawei
title: Taejae University Reimagines Education Around the Learner
